{"type":"text","timestamp":1775862519529,"sessionID":"ses_28659db9ffferpMTMlg4pOfnhF","part":{"id":"prt_d79a77436001mzRb8hISu6XFqa","messageID":"msg_d79a7672e001qSPzYttqLCt664","sessionID":"ses_28659db9ffferpMTMlg4pOfnhF","type":"text","text":"Based on my analysis of the AR-017 proposal, tasks, and implementation:\n\n## AR-017 — PicoD JWT 中间件 Archive\n\n### ✅ Completed\n\n**Core Implementation:**\n- `crypto.go` — RSA key handling (LoadPublicKey, LoadPublicKeyFromBase64, ParsePEM, GenerateKeyPair, EncodePublicKeyToPEM)\n- `jwt.go` — JWT token validation (Claims struct, Validate, ParseAndValidate, VerifySignature)\n- `auth_errors.go` — Authentication error types and HTTP status mapping\n- `middleware.go` — JWT HTTP middleware (JWTMiddleware, NewJWTMiddleware, Middleware, extractToken)\n- `config.go` — Auth configuration fields (AuthMode, PublicKeyPEM, SkipPaths) loaded from env vars\n\n**Tests:**\n- `crypto_test.go` — RSA key tests (all passing ✓)\n- `jwt_test.go` — JWT validation tests\n- `middleware_test.go` — Middleware tests (valid/missing/invalid/expired tokens, skip paths)\n- Integration tests present in `integration_test.go`\n\n### ⏸ Deferred\n\n**Configuration:**\n- `Config.Validate()` for auth config validation — not implemented\n- `ParseAuthFlags()` command-line flag parsing — not implemented\n- `PICOD_AUTH_CLOCK_SKEW` environment variable — not implemented\n\n**PicoD Integration:**\n- `PicoD` struct auth fields (authMode, publicKey) — not added\n- `WithAuthMode()` / `WithPublicKey()` functional options — not implemented\n- `SetupHTTPServer()` with JWT middleware integration — not implemented\n- Command-line flags (`-auth`, `-public-key`, `-skip-paths`, `-clock-skew`) — not implemented\n\n**Documentation:**\n- Go doc comments on public types — minimal\n- Usage examples in doc comments — not added\n- `pkg/picod/README.md` updates — not done\n- Security documentation (key management, rotation) — not done\n\n**Test Gaps:**\n- `TestConfig_Validate_AuthMode` — not implemented (no Validate method)\n- Some integration tests may be incomplete\n\n**Note:** Existing test failures (`TestExecutor_WithTimeout`, `TestPicoD_Integration_*`) are unrelated to JWT middleware — they appear to be pre-existing issues with command execution tests.","time":{"start":1775862519527,"end":1775862519527}}}
